path:addable-pages:square:desc: Optimize your payment processing with our SquareUp Integration. Manage transactions, and monitor invoice data all within our platform. Elevate your experience with the power and convenience of Square at your service.
path:addable-pages:gdrive:desc: Streamline your document access and collaboration with our Google Drive Integration. Dive into a unified workflow with Google Drive at your command.
path:addable-pages:gmail:desc: Elevate your workflow with our Gmail Integration. Directly connect your inbox, streamline communications, and manage tasks without ever leaving our platform. Simplify, integrate, and achieve more with Gmail at your fingertips.
path:addable-pages:github:desc: Sync your codebase with ease using our GitHub Integration. Manage repositories, track commits, and collaborate on development projects directly from our platform. path:addable-pages:upwork:desc: Bridge the gap between freelance management and your projects. With our Upwork Integration, effortlessly monitor your freelancers, all within our platform.
path:addable-pages:iframe:desc: Expand your content capabilities with our Additional <iframe> feature. Seamlessly embed external content, widgets, or tools within our platform, providing a richer, more interactive experience for your users. Simplify integration and elevate your presentation with versatile <iframe> options.
path:addable-pages:waveapps:desc: Streamline your accounting and invoicing with our WaveApps Integration. Manage your finances, track expenses, and monitor invoices all within our platform. Simplify your workflow and elevate your experience with WaveApps at your service.
path:addable-pages:figma-design:desc: Seamlessly integrate and display your Figma design files directly on our platform. Enhance your presentations and collaborations with our easy-to-use Figma Embed feature.
